    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Hughes Woodfire Pizzeria is a family-run business dedicated to bringing the authentic taste of Naples to your table. Our pizzas are made with the finest imported ingredients, dough fermented for 48 hours, and baked in a traditional woodfire oven at over 900°F for that signature blistered crust and smoky flavor.</p>
        <p>Founded in 2023 by pizza enthusiast Alex Hughes, we blend Italian tradition with local flair to create unforgettable meals. Join us for a slice of Italy!</p>
    </section>

